bamtools
------------------------------------------
BamTools provides both a programmer's API and an end-user's toolkit for
handling BAM files.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.0-1
  libbamtools-devel-2.5.1-1bl2
  libbamtools2.5.1-2.5.1-1bl2
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  libjsoncpp-devel-1.8.4-1
  libjsoncpp19-1.8.4-1
  libstdc++6-7.4.0-1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1
  zlib-devel-1.2.11-1
  zlib0-1.2.11-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.14.5-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools/archive/v2.5.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bamtools-2.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bamtools-2.5.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bamtools-2.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bamtools-2.5.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbamtools2.5.1-2.5.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbamtools-devel-2.5.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(bamtools)
  /usr/bin/bamtools.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/bamtools.README
  /usr/share/doc/bamtools/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/bamtools/README

(libbamtools2.5.1)
  /usr/bin/cygbamtools-2.5.1.dll

(libbamtools-devel)
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamAlgorithms.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamAlignment.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamAux.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamConstants.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamIndex.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamMultiReader.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamReader.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamWriter.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/IBamIODevice.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamConstants.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamHeader.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamProgram.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamProgramChain.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamReadGroup.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamReadGroupDictionary.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamSequence.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/SamSequenceDictionary.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/algorithms/Sort.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/api_global.h
  /usr/include/bamtools/shared/bamtools_global.h
  /usr/lib/libbamtools.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/bamtools-1.pc

